{"tid":737595,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美光禁令不痛癢？外資：北京怕川普直接禁了半導體設備","createTime":"2018-07-11T03:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T04:48:19.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"87cc7337db8dffb6a790cd93aad7a7ca374131d6","tid":737595,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:11:16.000Z","msg":"美光禁令不痛癢？外資：北京怕川普直接禁了半導體設備<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2018/07/10/micron-china-prohibition-semiconductor-equipment/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2Fmicron-china-prohibition-semiconductor-equipment%2F&d=5I9w6mDduBvuu2O%2Fz0Jch75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=6c7e0055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2018/07/10/micron-china-prohibition-semiconductor-equipment/</a><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易大戰爆發，中國率先眨眼了嗎？從美光（Micron Technology）記憶體產品在中國面臨禁售、影響層面卻不多的情況，或可看出端倪。<br />\n<br />\nbarron&rsquo;<a href=\"http://s.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.com&d=5I9w6mDduBvuu2O%2Fz0Jch75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=c07a18f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">s.com</a> 9 日兩篇文章報導，瑞士信貸分析師 John Pitzer 發表研究報告指出，美光僅有價值 8,000 萬美元的部分產品遭陸方禁售，該公司還重申本季財報展望不變，顯示中國法院的行動根本不痛不癢，懲戒幾乎無意義。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Pitzer 直指，中國法院在動作時綁手綁腳，意味著中美貿易大戰升溫，已讓北京開始擔心，攸關中國半導體發展的半導體資本設備，也會遭美國下達禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n根據摩根士丹利分析師 Joseph Moore、Craig Hettenbach 的說法，中國每年需在半導體設備上花費數百億美元，才能成功打造自有的晶片業。<br />\n<br />\n不少分析人士認為美國也許會選在某個時間點禁止美國半導體設備商向中國出口產品，直接阻撓北京取得需要的設備。<br />\n</span><br />\n聯電甫於台北時間 7 月 3 日晚間公告，中國福州中級人民法院已對美光發出禁令，要求美光在聯電侵權訴訟期間，停止西安、上海分公司共 26 項產品的生產及銷售，這當中包括 DRAM 和 NAND 等相關品項。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69326fa2a164e6213e7bb92aeb77db5daa7e644","tid":737595,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c1e47360f9058be7c80a1ac71a7298c854ae5a","tid":737595,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:39:30.000Z","msg":"點都好 贏國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec55a2479f0b93da131059dec99e4e791e0c1d37","tid":737595,"uid":66496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:40:41.000Z","msg":"冇半導體 <br />\n贏國d big data,芝麻信用果堆垃圾點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e73e1648aa87058a79f37045bacdc55f3262592","tid":737595,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:44:13.000Z","msg":"其實禁制令唔係話出就出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5780e7a53223745fa93a500599e7c29407ad0856","tid":737595,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:48:19.000Z","msg":"又可以自煮燃髮 又贏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}